  "title": "Staff Nurse (In-House Company Clinic | Industrial Area) - 5 days / Office Hour [0580]",
  "description": "<p>Salary Range: $3,000 - $3,500<br />Working Hour: 5 days, Mon to Fri 8.00am to 5.35pm(Pioneer)<br />Working Location: Pioneer Industrial Area</p><p><strong>Job Responsibilities:</strong></p><ul><li>Provision of basic nursing duties</li><li>Provide medical care and counselling to patients</li><li>Perform basic triage, assist in minor procedures</li><li>Registration of patients & dispensing of medication</li><li>Management of patient’s medical records</li><li>Perform clinical and administrative duties such as to schedule patient appointments and registration</li><li>Handle phone calls and enquiries</li><li>Booking of referral appointments</li><li>Any other duties as assigned by the Head Nurse</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>SNB Registered</li><li>Diploma in Nursing</li></ul><p><br />The Supreme HR Advisory Pte. Ltd || 14C7279</p><p>Chua Jie Ying (Cai Jie Ying), Evelynn || EA Personnel License R24120580</p>",
